nodes.text: Seaweed came from the ocean and could be a type of foodstuff. The Lanai served spiced seaweed at the Festival of Return on Ahch-To. When Poe Dameron and Finn attended Nifera Shu's birthday party, a variety of seafoods were displayed on beds of multicolored seaweed in keeping with the ocean theme. Seaweed clung to Luke Skywalker's T-65B X-wing starfighter when he raised it from the waters of Ahch-To after its years of submersion.
